    • Method Detail

      • populateResourceNarrative

        boolean populateResourceNarrative​(FhirContext theFhirContext,
                                  IBaseResource theResource)
        Generate any narratives for the given resource that have applicable templates, and populates the appropriate field(s). This almost always means the Resource.text.narrative field, but for some resource types it can mean other fields (e.g. Composition.
        Returns:
        Returns true if a narrative was actually generated
